Welcome to the homepage for AntiKlexos.
This page is still under construction.
But before you leave, you should know that antiklexos is the opposite of klexos.

Klexos is a Greek word that means «fixation on the past.» This here is antiklexos. We represent all that is opposed to this fixation so that you live in a present full of adventure.


I’d like to join the workshop waitlist
